text: KDFJ-LP (105.9 FM) is a FCC licensed low power FM radio station serving Fairbanks, Alaska and parts of North Pole, Alaska. The station is owned and managed by Calvary Chapel North Star (CCNS). It airs a Religious radio format. ==References== *http://www.fccinfo.com/CMDProEngine.php?sCurrentService=FM&tabSearchType;=Appl&sAppIDNumber;=1588806 ==External links== *CCNS Homepage * Category:2014 establishments in Alaska DFJ-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 DFJ-LP DFJ-LP
